    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im stuck on this bathroom remodel. i just finished hanging the drywall but the seams are looking a bit rough. what's the best way to tape and mud them so i don't end up with visible lines after i sand it down?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
